item.title: Getting server posted on the status page
item.dc:creator: @Harleyscape_owner Harleyscape owner
item.description:
@Harleyscape_owner wrote:

go to http://www.flashspace.us/serverstatus.php?action=register then type in name,ip and port then click go or ok or something, but you gotta make sure that you have your server running before you try to put on server status page or it wont let you put it up.
